.

1. *Govoriš* da ćeš me zvati kasnije? (Are you saying that you'll call me later?)
2. Da li *govoriš* pravu istinu? (Are you speaking the truth?)
3. Nisam siguran da ti *govoriš* istinu. (I'm not sure that you're telling the truth.)
4. *Govoriš* li mi ono što misliš? (Are you telling me what you think?)
5. On ne *govoriš* nikome o tome. (He is not telling anyone about it.)
6. *Govoriš* li to ozbiljno? (Are you speaking seriously?)
7. Ona se ponaša tako kao da *govoriš* istinu. (She behaves as if she's speaking the truth.)
8. *Govoriš* li ti isto kao što misliš? (Are you saying the same thing as you think?)